sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant CM as chat.message
    participant MT as messages.transform
    participant TEB as tool.execute.before
    participant TEA as tool.execute.after
    participant O as Orchestrator (LLM)
    participant SA as Sub-Agent

    Note over U,SA: === CLASSIFICATION PHASE ===
    U->>CM: "make a tank battle game"
    CM->>CM: classify() → canvas-game, high confidence
    CM->>CM: fsm: idle → classifying → awaiting_hitl
    CM->>O: HITL confirmation (original message held)

    U->>CM: "ok"
    CM->>CM: parseResponse() → confirm
    CM->>CM: fsm: awaiting_hitl → discovery
    CM->>CM: lock classification
    CM->>O: original message + classification context

    Note over U,SA: === DISCOVERY PHASE ===
    O->>O: Analysis complete
    Note over O: fsm: discovery → build (light task)

    Note over U,SA: === BUILD PHASE ===
    O->>TEB: task(@forcoding-builder, prompt)
    TEB->>TEB: phaseLock.check() → OK (can dispatch builder)
    TEB->>TEB: preBuildGate.validate() → OK (all checks pass)
    TEB->>SA: dispatch builder
    SA-->>TEA: output

    TEA->>TEA: truncationRecovery.detect() → OK
    TEA->>TEA: postBuildValidator.check() → OK
    TEA->>TEA: autoAdvance(build → audit)
    MT->>O: [ForCoding] Builder complete. Dispatch Auditor.

    Note over U,SA: === AUDIT PHASE ===
    O->>TEB: task(@forcoding-auditor, prompt)
    TEB->>TEB: verify state === audit
    TEB->>SA: dispatch auditor
    SA-->>TEA: output: VERDICT: VALIDATED

    TEA->>TEA: parseAuditorVerdict() → VALIDATED
    TEA->>TEA: cycleDetector.reset()
    TEA->>TEA: autoAdvance(audit → rsi)
    MT->>O: [ForCoding] Auditor passed. Begin RSI.

    Note over U,SA: === RSI PHASE ===
    O->>O: Screenshots + visual verification
    Note over O: fsm: rsi → done

    Note over U: Task complete
